<subSubSection pageId="40" pageNumber="373" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="40.[132,777,503,784]" box="[132,232,503,529]" pageId="40" pageNumber="373">REMARKS</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[132,777,503,784]" pageId="40" pageNumber="373">All the examined specimens have a broken peristome (presence/absence of lip thickening not observable).</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[132,777,503,784]" pageId="40" pageNumber="373">
<taxonomicName authority="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio, 2022" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[155,272,598,624]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="lozoueti" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[155,272,598,624]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="373">B. lozoueti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[282,345,598,624]" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
differs from 
<taxonomicName authority="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio, 2022" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[497,621,599,624]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="tuamotu" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[497,621,599,624]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="373">B. tuamotu</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[631,694,598,624]" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
by the presence of weak thickenings at the intersections of the spiral cordlets with the axial ribs, absent in 
<taxonomicName authority="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio, 2022" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[580,700,662,687]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="tuamotu" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[580,700,662,687]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="373">B. tuamotu</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[708,770,662,688]" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
; 
<taxonomicName authority="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio, 2022" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[132,241,693,719]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="lozoueti" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[132,241,693,719]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="373">B. lozoueti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[247,304,694,720]" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
has a slightly convex base vs slightly concave in 
<taxonomicName authority="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio, 2022" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[161,279,726,751]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="tuamotu" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[161,279,726,751]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="373">B. tuamotu</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[285,343,726,752]" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and on average has more numerous and finer axial ribs (22.4 vs 
<quantity box="[384,462,757,784]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.445" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" unit="in" value="17.5">17.5 in</quantity>
<taxonomicName authority="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio, 2022" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[469,588,758,783]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="tuamotu" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[469,588,758,783]" italics="true" pageId="40" pageNumber="373">B. tuamotu</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[595,656,757,784]" pageId="40" pageNumber="373" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
).
</paragraph>
